headline.print_headline: Coast Guard Calls Off Ocean Search for California Guardsman
headline.main: Coast Guard Calls Off Ocean Search for California Guardsman

lead_paragraph: The U.S. Coast Guard has called off a search for an off-duty member of the California Air National Guard who was swept into the ocean while he was fishing near Monterey, officials said on Wednesday.
